    "custom_faq_NGMAhA": {
      "type": "custom_faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CjyQyH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-img": "shopify://shop_images/Layer_1_58a1c154-4189-4cce-91af-27256023f0ec.png",
            "faq-title": "Returns, Refunds and Exchanges",
            "questions": "What is your Returns & Exchange Policy?##How can I place a return or exchange request?##How are return requests processed?##What is the return policy for items bought during a sale period? ##How will I receive the refund for my returned product? ##When will the refund amount be credited to my account?  ##I placed a COD order, how will I get my refund? ##What will happen if I do not accept my order while it is out for delivery?##How long does it take to exchange my product?##Can I do more than 1 exchange?",
            "answers": "We offer a hassle-free 7-days return and exchange policy from the date of delivery. Refunds are initiated within 5 days after the return items are picked up. Please note that embroidery/engraving orders are not eligible for returns and exchanges. ##To place a return or exchange request, please visit <a class=\"RD_track\" href=\"https://knyamed.com/pages/returns-exchanges\" target=\"_blank\">Return &amp; Exchange Page.</a> Our team will review and approve your request within 3 working days. Once approved, we will arrange pick up for the items within 2 working days.##Once your return request is approved, our logistics partner will pick up the items within 2 working days. The returned item will undergo quality checks, and refunds will be initiated within 5 days after the items are picked up.##Any items bought during the sale period do not qualify for a return. They are final sale items.##For prepaid orders, the refund amount will be credited back to the original payment method after a deduction of FLAT Rs 100 as a reverse shipment fee. For Cash on Delivery orders, you will receive store credits in the form of a Knya gift card sent to your registered email address.##Refunds are typically initiated within 5 days after the returned item passes quality checks. The entire process usually takes 7-10 working days. ##For COD orders, you will receive store credits in the form of a Knya gift card, which will be sent to your registered email address. Please note that COD handling charges paid at the time of placing the order are non-refundable.##As a standard practice, we attempt delivery 3 times, and we try reaching out to you. In case the order is not accepted, a standard deduction of INR 150 towards shipping charges will be applied during the refund process. This refund will be credited to you in the form of a Gift card. ##The exchange process starts after the pickup of the old order. Typically, the entire process, from placing the exchange request to receiving the new product, takes 7-10 working days.##Due to operational difficulties, we will only be able to exchange your order once. Our customer service agents are there to help you choose the right fit for you."
          }
        },
